OL,3,CSir Lindsay Hoyle: 'People should
OL,4,Cdecide if Jersey gets elected Speaker'
OL,6,FThe Bailiff's office is more than 800
OL,7,Fyears old, with Sir Timothy's deputy,
OL,8,FRobert MacRae, announced to succeed
OL,9,Fhim.
OL,11,FHowever, there have been calls to
OL,12,Freplace the role with an elected
OL,13,FSpeaker like the UK - a scheduled vote
OL,14,Fon the issue was withdrawn late last
OL,15,Fyear due to a lack of political
OL,16,Fsupport.
